# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` in the project root for local Cloudflare Pages
# Functions (e.g. `wrangler pages dev`). Never commit `.dev.vars`.
#
# Production: set the same names as encrypted secrets in the Cloudflare dashboard
# (Workers & Pages → your project → Settings → Variables and Secrets).

# --- Google OAuth (server-side only; not VITE_) ---
# Use a Google OAuth 2.0 Web client (Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials).
# Authorized redirect URIs must include your callback URL, for example:
#   https://localhost:3000/api/auth/callback
#   https://YOUR-SUBDOMAIN.pages.dev/api/auth/callback
#   https://your-custom-domain/api/auth/callback
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
